// Title: Token Impersonation Detection
// Description: Detects creation of access tokens for another user which may indicate credential misuse.
// Data Source: SecurityEvent
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0006 - Credential Access
//   Technique: T1134.001 - Access Token Manipulation
// Severity: High

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 4672 or EventID == 4648
| project TimeGenerated, Account, Computer, Activity
| order by TimeGenerated desc